These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, 7up, sprite
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, lemon, orange, cabbage
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, rock-climbing, card-games, magic-tricks
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, accountant, coach, analyst
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, gospel, blues, hip-hop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, water-polo, badminton, handball
 1. the analyst is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is the fan of d&b##1
 3. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 4. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is the person eating cabbage##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 7. the coach is between the person who's sport is swimming and the fan of hip-hop##2
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the fan of d&b is on the right of the librarian##1
10. the person who's sport is swimming is between the coach and the person eating cabbage##2
11. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
12. the analyst is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
13. the fan of blues is between the fan of gospel and the person who's hobby is card-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | sprite        | hot-chocolate       | 7up  | cola |
| Food          | cabbage     | orange         | lemon     | nectarine    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing  | sudoku      | card-games   | magic-tricks     |
| Job           | accountant | librarian | coach   | analyst     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | blues         | d&b | hip-hop         |
| Sport         | handball     | swimming     | water-polo  | badminton       |

