.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, lemonade, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, board-games, fishing, magic-tricks
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, family, superhero, drama
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, pop, country, jazz
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, turkish, japanese, indian
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, boat, trike, van
 1. the turkish is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person driving the jet-ski##2
 2. the indian is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the thai##1
 4. the turkish is between the person drinking juice and the person driving the trike##2
 5. the fan of reggae is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the fan of country is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 8. the person driving the trike is between the person watching zombie movies and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
 9. the person watching family movies is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
10. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
11. the fan of reggae is the person watching superhero movies##1
12. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
13. the japanese is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
14. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea    | iced-tea       | lemonade   | juice |
| Hobby         | video-games     | fishing   | magic-tricks    | board-games  |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie    | superhero | family   | drama     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | reggae       | pop | country        |
| Nationality   | indian | japanese   | turkish     | thai    |
| Transport     | boat       | trike        | van      | jet-ski        |

