.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, sprite, cola, almond-milk
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, mango, apricot, artichoke
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, british, indian, french
4 different pets are kept: frog, goat, cat, chinchilla
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, cricket, lacrosse, parkour
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, train, snowmobile, trike
 1. the british is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 2. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 4. the person eating mango is on the left of the french##1
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is the person drinking cola##1
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the trike is between the indian and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 8. the person drinking sprite is the owner of the goat##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is between the person driving the trike and the owner of the frog##2
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is the person driving the snowmobile##1
12. the person eating apricot is the person driving the train##1
13. the owner of the cat is between the person eating raspberry and the british##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola      | coffee        | sprite | almond-milk      |
| Food          | raspberry   | apricot       | mango          | artichoke   |
