The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, superhero, satire, sports
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, argentine, canadian, australian
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, bus, skateboard, bike
 1. the person drinking juice is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the canadian##2
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the pilot##1
 3. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 5. the australian is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the analyst is on the left of the nigerian##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is the person watching sports movies##1
 9. the person driving the motorbike is between the analyst and the person who's hobby is motorbiked-games##2
10. the canadian is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is motorbiked-games is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
12. the manager is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
13. the person drinking mirinda is the person drinking mirinda##1
14. the person who's hobby is traveling is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
