 9. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
12. the turkish is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
