.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, sprite, hot-chocolate
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, cranberry, papaya, cherry
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, software-developer, police-officer, scientist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, d&b, gospel, dubstep
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, canadian, indonesian, chinese
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hedgehog, cat, ferret
 1. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the colombian##1
 2. the indonesian is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the police-officer##1
 5. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
 6. the fan of dubstep is between the engineer and the person eating cherry##2
 7. the chinese is on the left of the fan of rock##1
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
 9. the chinese is the person eating pomegranate##1
10. the software-developer is the owner of the ferret##1
11. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
12. the person drinking juice is the owner of the cat##1
13. the fan of gospel is on the right of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate        | sprite     | coffee        | juice    |
| Food          | papaya     | cranberry   | pomegranate   | cherry |
| Job           | scientist | engineer  | software-developer | police-officer |
| Music-Genre   | d&b            | gospel    | dubstep        | rock  |
| Nationality   | indonesian          | colombian | chinese      | canadian  |
| Pet           | hedgehog          | goldfish     | ferret      | cat      |

