.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, cola, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, puzzles, reading, fishing
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, fisherman, pilot, social-worker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, scientific, mystery, zombie
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, japanese, italian, mexican
4 different pets are kept: cat, goat, guinea-pig, rabbit
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is the mexican##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the software-developer##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the japanese##1
 6. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 7. the person drinking cola is between the pilot and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
 8. the pilot is the italian##1
 9. the person watching zombie movies is between the owner of the rabbit and the italian##2
10. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
11. the social-worker is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
12. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
13. the person who's hobby is reading is the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk        | cola      | sprite | hot-chocolate       |
| Hobby         | reading | singing | fishing   | puzzles   |
| Job           | pilot | social-worker     | fisherman        | software-developer   |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific     | zombie    | action | mystery    |
| Nationality   | italian      | japanese      | mexican      | australian |
| Pet           | cat      | goat    | rabbit       | guinea-pig  |

