.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, coffee, iced-tea, milk
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, zucchini, corn, pomegranate
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, paramedic, doctor, firefighter
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, hip-hop, jazz, rock
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, russian, colombian, italian
4 different pets are kept: snake, mouse, cat, fish
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 2. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the doctor##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the social-worker is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 6. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
 7. the fan of rock is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 8. the person eating pomegranate is between the malaysian and the owner of the mouse##2
 9. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
10. the italian is on the right of the person drinking water##1
11. the owner of the snake is the firefighter##1
12. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
13. the fan of d&b is between the social-worker and the owner of the snake##2
14. the firefighter is on the left of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |       3        |     4     |
| Beverage      | milk      | water | coffee       | iced-tea   |
| Food          | zucchini   | corn          | pomegranate           | strawberry |
| Job           | social-worker     | paramedic    | firefighter | doctor     |
| Music-Genre   | rock   | d&b          | hip-hop         | jazz     |
| Nationality   | russian    | malaysian      | italian       | colombian    |
| Pet           | fish | cat       | snake         | mouse  |

