.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-18::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, lettuce, garlic, nectarine
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, hiking, gardening, rock-climbing
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, paramedic, lawyer, coach
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, superhero, spy, horror
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, indonesian, american, indian
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, taxi, jet-ski, scooter
 1. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the lawyer##1
 2. the person watching spy movies is between the coach and the accountant##2
 3. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the paramedic##1
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the canadian##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person driving the skateboard and the indonesian##2
 7. the person driving the scooter is between the canadian and the person driving the taxi##2
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is the coach##1
11. the paramedic is on the left of the indonesian##1
12. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
13. the american is the person eating zucchini##1
14. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |       3       |      4      |
| Food          | nectarine     | garlic        | lettuce         | zucchini   |
| Hobby         | singing     | gardening     | hiking    | rock-climbing |
| Job           | paramedic  | coach      | lawyer | accountant   |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | horror | spy        | epic       |
| Nationality   | indian    | indonesian     | canadian    | american     |
| Transport     | taxi | scooter       | jet-ski         | skateboard         |

