.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, cola, sprite
There 4 different types of food: apple, pepper, cucumber, artichoke
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, collecting, skydiving
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, writer, architect, videographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, scientific, spy, time-travel
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, british, nigerian
 1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the architect##1
 2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
 3. the argentine is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 5. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the brazilian##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the analyst##1
 7. the writer is on the right of the analyst##1
 8. the person drinking milk is the person watching horror movies##1
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is the british##1
10. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the writer##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
12. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person drinking sprite and the architect##2
13. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | cola         | sprite       | milk         |
| Food          | apple | pepper  | cucumber        | artichoke         |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing | dancing     | skydiving   |
| Job           | architect | analyst  | writer | videographer |
| Movie-Genre   | spy  | time-travel     | scientific       | horror   |
| Nationality   | british | brazilian   | nigerian        | argentine       |

