.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, milk, soy-milk, juice
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, cucumber, nectarine, plum
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, rock-climbing, video-games, camping
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, thai, japanese, malaysian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, water-polo, soccer, ice-hockey
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, train, ship, bike
 1. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
 3. the indonesian is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
 5. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the malaysian is the person eating cucumber##1
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person driving the trike##1
 8. the person driving the train is the person eating plum##1
 9. the thai is the person driving the bike##1
10. the malaysian is on the right of the japanese##1
11. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person drinking milk and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
12. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
13. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | tea | juice     | soy-milk  | milk |
| Food          | raspberry     | nectarine     | cucumber | plum  |
| Hobby         | camping   | board-games | rock-climbing  | video-games   |
| Nationality   | thai         | japanese   | malaysian   | indonesian |
| Sport         | water-polo       | soccer    | ice-hockey   | weightlifting |
| Transport     | bike        | trike   | ship   | train      |

 